cast.overview: 70-year-old widower Ben Whittaker has discovered that retirement isn't all it's cracked up to be. Seizing an opportunity to get back in the game, he becomes a senior intern at an online fashion site, founded and run by Jules Ostin.
cast.title: The Intern

details.biography:
Elliot Villar (born June 6, 1980) is an American theater and screen actor. He made his Broadway debut in 2011 as part of the original cast of War Horse. He is perhaps best known for his role as Fernando Vera in the USA Network show Mr. Robot.

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
details.name: Elliot Villar
details.place_of_birth: New York City, New York, USA
